---
import { Markdown } from 'astro/components';
---
<article class="intro-section">
    <section class="flex flex-col personal-card md:flex-row">
        <div class="w-4/12 personal-card_left">
            <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold personal-card_name top-8 md:top-1/4 md:text-7xl -left-3 md:-left-10 lg:-left-24">
                <p class="">Jesus</p>
                <p class="mb-0 pl-14">Guerrero</p>
                <p class="mt-5 text-sm pl-14">
                    Web developer / Software Engineer / Creator
                </p>
            </h1>
        </div>

        <div class="px-10 mt-48 space-y-10 text-lg personal-card_body md:space-y-5 md:px-20 md:mt-0 md:w-8/12">
            <Markdown>         
                I'm a system engineer, web developer from Dominican Republic who is 
                passionate about programming in general, web development and [Vue.js](https://v3.vuejs.org). Currently working at 
                [MCTekk](https://mctekk.com) mostly doing frontend development.
            </Markdown>
            <p class="hidden md:block">
                I love to learn new things, share knowledge and create (apps, (a try of) poetry ). 
                When not, I am singing Bob Marley's songs.
            </p>

            <Markdown>
                Find me on [Twitter](https://github.com/antfu/vitesse), [Github]() or [Hashnode](https://freesgen.hashnode.dev).
            </Markdown>
        </div>
    </section>
</article>

<style lang="scss">
    article {
        background-color: var(--darken-primary-color);
        color: var(--text-color);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100vh;
    }
    
    section.personal-card {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        height: 80%;
        width: 80%;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin: auto;
        position: relative;
        background: var(--primary-color); 

        &:after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            right: 20%;
            height: 0;
            width: 0;
            border-right: 50px solid transparent;
            border-left: 50px solid transparent;
            border-top: 50px solid transparent;
            border-bottom: 30px solid var(--darken-primary-color);
        }

        .personal-card_name {
            color: dodgerblue;
            position: absolute;
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        section.personal-card {
            width: 90%;
            height: 95%;

             &:after {
                bottom: 0;
                right: 20%;
                height: 0;
                width: 0;
                border-right: 20px solid transparent;
                border-left: 20px solid transparent;
                border-top: 20px solid transparent;
                border-bottom: 16px solid var(--darken-primary-color);
            }
        }
    }
</style>
